    com.guardtime.ksi.tree
    This package contains classes and interfaces used to build a hash tree.

      interface  TreeBuilder<N extends TreeNode>
      This interface is used to build binary tree which every node in the tree has at most two children.
      Classes in com.guardtime.ksi.tree that implement TreeNode 
      Modifier and Type Class and Description
      class  ImprintNode
      This class represents a hash tree node which every non-leaf node is labelled with the hash of the labels or values (in case of leaves) of its child nodes.
